### Library Management System API - GET Requests

### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api

### Get All Students
GET {{baseUrl}}/students

### Get All Books
GET {{baseUrl}}/books

### Get All Departments
GET {{baseUrl}}/departments

### Get All Publishers
GET {{baseUrl}}/publishers

### Get All Courses
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses

### Get All Staff
GET {{baseUrl}}/staff

### Get All Locations
GET {{baseUrl}}/locations

### Get All Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/status

### Get Student by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/students/1

### Get Book by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/books/1

### Get Department by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/departments/1

### Get Publisher by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/publishers/1
